headline: Apartments.com Releases Multifamily Rent Report for the First Quarter of 2025
summary: ARLINGTON, Va., April 02, 2025--Today, Apartments.com – an online marketplace of CoStar Group – published an in-depth report on multifamily rent trends for the first quarter of 2025.

headline: Reflecting On Data & Business Process Services Stocks’ Q4 Earnings: CoStar (NASDAQ:CSGP)
summary: Wrapping up Q4 earnings, we look at the numbers and key takeaways for the data & business process services stocks, including CoStar (NASDAQ:CSGP) and its peers.
